SUMMER VENGEANCE MATCH
DIA ZERVA
Iron Maiden
HT: 5'5
WT: 145lbs
Lifetime record (1-1)
Ranked 6th
AMBER RAYNE
Rogue
HT: 5'3
WT: 115lbs
Lifetime record (3-3)
Ranked 11th
Welcome to the second annual Summer Vengeance elimination tournament where the top sixteen Season Five wrestlers battle it out to see who will be the overall Ultimate Surrender champion for 2008.
Dia Zerva is new to US, coming in late in the season. However she has shown she is a powerhouse and a power to be reckoned with. She has strength, size, speed, and most importantly, excellent mat experience and skills.
Amber Rayne was last year's Featherweight Champion. A spunky little fighter that is 100% go and fury on the mat. Tiny maybe, but ferocious to the extreme.
Join today for the only non-scripted real sexual wresting on the net!
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE CONTINUES! This is the third elimination match of the second round.
